      <title>1.0.6</title>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Enhancements:</strong>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Queue Clipboard Redesign:</strong> The Queue Clipboard window has been redesigned for a better user experience.</li>
                <li><strong>Custom Separator:</strong> Added options to customize the separator when pasting multiple items.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Bug Fixes:</strong>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Window Height:</strong> Fixed unexpected window shrinking; it now respects your preferred size.</li>
                <li><strong>Settings Window:</strong> Fixed app quitting when closing Settings; now stays in the menu bar.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
